  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\ngeth v1.13.0\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n`--snapshot=false` disables snapshotting\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nIt is ignored since default sync mode is now snap and that causes the snapshot flag to be overridden \r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n`--snapshot=false`\r\n\r\non the other hand\r\n`--syncmode full --snapshot=false` stops snapshotting\r\n",
